GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Antithesis> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Antithesis> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Antithesis> ;
    narr:childCount "84"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "6373bbeac4587c55b0019c704a3872442633ced3" ;
    narr:narration """This hub catalogs antithesis as the dominant rhetorical and structural device across the aswritten corpus, spanning product strategy, architecture, fundraising, and design philosophy. The device appears in several distinct modes: as [binary opposition organizing entire documents](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_AgentSim_Antithesis) (decay vs. depreciation, procedural vs. human-driven); as [aphoristic compression](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_IntelligenceVsPerspective) distilling complex reframes into single punchy sentences; as [before/after rename documentation](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_AntithesisBeforeAfter_Distillation) marking strategic pivots by naming the superseded framing; and as [three-axis counter-positioning against AGI](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_SII_ThreeAxisAntithesis) at maximum compression density. A dated shift appears by June 2026: [the 'X, not Y' sentence-closing pattern is explicitly prohibited](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_NoXNotYAntithesis) as momentum-killing, with [the prescriptive position](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_NoXNotY) directing that contrast carrying load-bearing meaning be rebuilt through momentum structures instead. This prohibition coexists with continued heavy use of antithesis at the structural level — [architectural documents](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_AntithesisStructure), [sales framing](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_AntithesisTriggers), and [design arguments](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_PerspectiveOrdering_Antithesis) all remain antithesis-organized. The device also functions as [decision taxonomy](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_FableWindowAntithesisPattern) (dissolved/deferred/rejected) and as [skeptic-preservation structure](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_DavidNolen_SkepticalVoiceContrast), where the opposing voice is held verbatim rather than smoothed away.""" ;
